Name: Smoked Meat Stew
AttributesDescription: Increases Resonance Liberation DMG Bonus of all Resonators in the team by 40% for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
BgDescription: Thin slices of meat smoked over Creeping Torchpine needles are stewed together with the fermented drink, then served with mashed potatoes and a spoonful of Dusk Honeypot jam. The rich fat of the Kronapuff mingles with the firm, chewy Lemming meat, offering alternating waves of flavor. On a night when the cold wind cuts to the bone, one mouthful is enough to make you forget the coldness and the exhaustion that came with them.
